ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-kho-tho\/#Nhung_nguyen_nhan_gay_ra_tinh_trang_ga_kho_tho\" >Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-kho-tho\/#Ga_kho_tho_la_tien_de_cua_benh_gi\" >G\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ec7nh g\u00ec?<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-kho-tho\/#Lam_cach_nao_de_dieu_tri_ga_bi_kho_tho\" >L\u00e0m c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb g\u00e0 b\u1ecb kh\u00f3 th\u1edf?<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-kho-tho\/#Dieu_tri_benh_nhiem_trung_de_han_che_ga_kho_tho\" >\u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-kho-tho\/#Giai_quyet_nhung_van_de_lien_quan_den_duong_ho_hap_ga_kho_tho\" >Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-6\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-kho-tho\/#Dieu_tri_virus\" >\u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb virus<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-kho-tho\/#Kiem_soat_giun_san_cac_ky_sinh_trung\" >Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t giun s\u00e1n &amp; c\u00e1c k\u00fd sinh tr\u00f9ng<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-8\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-kho-tho\/#Cham_soc_ho_tro_ga_kho_tho\" >Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-9\" href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-kho-tho\/#Ket_luan\" >K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p><strong>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/ga-kho-tho\/\">g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf<\/a> c\u1ee7a <a href=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/\">Sv368<\/a> t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe n\u00e0y \u1edf gia c\u1ea7m, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n, nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 cho g\u00e0 b\u1ecb kh\u00f3 th\u1edf.<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Nhung_nguyen_nhan_gay_ra_tinh_trang_ga_kho_tho\"><\/span>Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 do nhi\u1ec1u nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n kh\u00e1c nhau, \u0111\u00f4i khi n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn m\u00e0 Sv368 mang \u0111\u1ebfn:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p: G\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1eafc c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh nh\u01b0 coryza, CRD (Chronic Respiratory Disease) ho\u1eb7c Mycoplasma gallisepticum, c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m, l\u00e0m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf s\u1ef1 th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Virus: C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i virus nh\u01b0 Newcastle disease hay avian influenza c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p v\u00e0 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 th\u1edf.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">S\u01b0ng m\u0169i &amp; c\u1ed5 h\u1ecdng: N\u1ebfu g\u00e0 b\u1ecb s\u01b0ng m\u0169i ho\u1eb7c c\u1ed5 h\u1ecdng do vi\u00eam nhi\u1ec5m, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u0103ng s\u1ef1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Parasites: M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 k\u00fd sinh tr\u00f9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i giun s\u00e1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p, g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c th\u1edf.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">B\u1ec7nh l\u00fd tim: G\u00e0 c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1eafc c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tim m\u1ea1ch, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f3 th\u1edf.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">B\u1ee5ng tr\u1ee9ng c\u0103ng \u0111\u1ea7y: \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi g\u00e0 m\u00e1i, n\u1ebfu b\u1ee5ng tr\u1ee9ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ebb tr\u1ee9ng, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u00e1p l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0 l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 th\u1edf cho g\u00e0.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">Thu\u1ed1c tr\u1eeb s\u00e2u &amp; h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t: S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c tr\u1eeb s\u00e2u ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c h\u00f3a ch\u1ea5t kh\u00f4ng an to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p cho g\u00e0.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3122\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3122\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3122 size-full\" title=\"G\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-1-1.jpg\" alt=\"Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf?\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-1-1.jpg?v=1709195457 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-1-1-300x150.jpg?v=1709195457 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-1-1-768x384.jpg?v=1709195457 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3122\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n g\u00e2y ra t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ga_kho_tho_la_tien_de_cua_benh_gi\"><\/span>G\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ec7nh g\u00ec?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>T\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i b\u1ec7nh kh\u00e1c nhau, \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh g\u00ec, c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c x\u00e9t nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m tra chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t b\u1edfi b\u00e1c s\u0129 th\u00fa y cao c\u1ea5p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ec7nh th\u01b0\u1eddng g\u1eb7p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng n\u00e0y:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">B\u1ec7nh coryza: Do vi khu\u1ea9n g\u00e2y n\u00ean, coryza l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ec7nh nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u0169i, m\u1eaft &amp; h\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a g\u00e0.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">CRD (Chronic Respiratory Disease): G\u00e2y ra b\u1edfi vi khu\u1ea9n Mycoplasma gallisepticum, CRD l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ec7nh nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p \u1edf g\u00e0.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">B\u1ec7nh Newcastle: Do virus Newcastle g\u00e2y ra, b\u1ec7nh n\u00e0y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p &amp; h\u1ec7 ti\u00eau h\u00f3a, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng nh\u01b0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">C\u00fam gia c\u1ea7m: B\u1ec7nh n\u00e0y do virus c\u00fam A g\u00e2y ra, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe, bao g\u1ed3m kh\u00f3 th\u1edf.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">B\u1ec7nh s\u01b0ng m\u0169i &amp; c\u1ed5 h\u1ecdng: C\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh nh\u01b0 s\u01b0ng m\u0169i v\u00e0 c\u1ed5 h\u1ecdng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f3 th\u1edf.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">B\u1ec7nh giun s\u00e1n: C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i giun s\u00e1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1ec7 h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a g\u00e0 v\u00e0 g\u00e2y ra c\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 th\u1edf.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">B\u1ec7nh l\u00fd tim: C\u00e1c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 tim c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng kh\u00f3 th\u1edf.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"1\">B\u1ec7nh c\u1ea5p t\u00ednh ho\u1eb7c m\u00e3n t\u00ednh: M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ec7nh kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0 b\u1ec7nh ti\u00eau ch\u1ea3y, b\u1ec7nh t\u1ee9c th\u00ec, ho\u1eb7c c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd \u0111a d\u1ea1ng kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f3 th\u1edf.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u1edbi tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng kh\u00f3 th\u1edf \u1edf g\u00e0, quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ch\u00fang \u0111\u1ebfn th\u0103m b\u00e1c s\u0129 th\u00fa y \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t li\u1ec7u ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb th\u00edch h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3123\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3123\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3123 size-full\" title=\"G\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-2-1.jpg\" alt=\"G\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ec7nh g\u00ec?\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-2-1.jpg?v=1709195457 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-2-1-300x150.jpg?v=1709195457 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-2-1-768x384.jpg?v=1709195457 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3123\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">G\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a b\u1ec7nh g\u00ec?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Lam_cach_nao_de_dieu_tri_ga_bi_kho_tho\"><\/span>L\u00e0m c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb g\u00e0 b\u1ecb kh\u00f3 th\u1edf?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn m\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia Sv368 mang \u0111\u1ebfn:<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dieu_tri_benh_nhiem_trung_de_han_che_ga_kho_tho\"><\/span>\u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>N\u1ebfu g\u00e0 m\u1eafc b\u1ec7nh coryza ho\u1eb7c CRD, b\u00e1c s\u0129 th\u00fa y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u00ea \u0111\u01a1n thu\u1ed1c kh\u00e1ng sinh nh\u01b0 oxytetracycline, enrofloxacin \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3124\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3124\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3124 size-full\" title=\"G\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-3-2.jpg\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-3-2.jpg?v=1709195458 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-3-2-300x150.jpg?v=1709195458 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-3-2-768x384.jpg?v=1709195458 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3124\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">\u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb b\u1ec7nh nhi\u1ec5m tr\u00f9ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Giai_quyet_nhung_van_de_lien_quan_den_duong_ho_hap_ga_kho_tho\"><\/span>Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi b\u1ec7nh l\u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p nh\u01b0 s\u01b0ng m\u0169i &amp; c\u1ed5 h\u1ecdng, vi\u1ec7c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng &amp; thu\u1ed1c kh\u00e1ng nhi\u1ec5m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1edf.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Dieu_tri_virus\"><\/span>\u0110i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb virus<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ec7nh do virus nh\u01b0 Newcastle disease ho\u1eb7c avian influenza, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 thu\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1ch ly g\u00e0 b\u1ec7nh v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c t\u1ed1t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c l\u00ean \u0111\u00e0n gia c\u1ea7m.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Kiem_soat_giun_san_cac_ky_sinh_trung\"><\/span>Ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t giun s\u00e1n &amp; c\u00e1c k\u00fd sinh tr\u00f9ng<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p>S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thu\u1ed1c ch\u1ed1ng giun s\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c k\u00fd sinh tr\u00f9ng n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c x\u00e9t nghi\u1ec7m x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u00e0 b\u1ecb nhi\u1ec5m s\u00e1n.<\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Cham_soc_ho_tro_ga_kho_tho\"><\/span>Ch\u0103m s\u00f3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">Cung c\u1ea5p m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1ea5m \u00e1p, tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i cho g\u00e0 b\u1ec7nh.<\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\" aria-level=\"2\">\u0110\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u00fang c\u00f3 n\u01b0\u1edbc &amp; th\u1ee9c \u0103n \u0111\u1ee7, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 \u0103n u\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a g\u00e0.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<figure id=\"attachment_3125\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-3125\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-3125 size-full\" title=\"G\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf\" src=\"http:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-4-1.jpg\" alt=\"L\u00e0m c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb g\u00e0 b\u1ecb kh\u00f3 th\u1edf?\" width=\"800\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-4-1.jpg?v=1709195459 800w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-4-1-300x150.jpg?v=1709195459 300w, https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/hinh-4-1-768x384.jpg?v=1709195459 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-3125\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">L\u00e0m c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb g\u00e0 b\u1ecb kh\u00f3 th\u1edf?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Ket_luan\"><\/span>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Sv368, ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf<span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y ra v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y cho \u0111\u00e0n gia c\u1ea7m. <\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 g\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u1edf c\u1ee7a Sv368 t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch c\u00e1c nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n v\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb cho t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe n\u00e0y \u1edf gia c\u1ea7m, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin chi ti\u1ebft v\u1ec1 c\u00e1ch ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n, nh\u1eadn bi\u1ebft tri\u1ec7u ch\u1ee9ng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p ch\u0103m s\u00f3c v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u [&#8230;]\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3125,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[6],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-2424","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-da-ga"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2424","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2424"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2424\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":5851,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2424\/revisions\/5851"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/3125"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2424"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=2424"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/sv368.dealer\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=2424"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}